### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3006
@tenantId = tenant-a

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3006/health

### List Workflows
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### Create Workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "Test Workflow",
  "description": "Quick test",
  "steps_json": {
    "steps": [
      {"step_id": "1", "step_name": "start", "type": "start-event", "next": "2"},
      {"step_id": "2", "step_name": "end", "type": "end-event"}
    ]
  },
  "created_by": "tester"
}

### Create Order (Trigger Workflow)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

{
  "customer_id": "cust-test",
  "items": [],
  "total": 15000
}
